&gt;&gt; Summary
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Enable a frame to signal the browser to include SameSite=None cookies in
&gt;&gt; first-party requests from sandboxed frames when third-party cookie (3PC)
&gt;&gt; restrictions are active using the allow-same-site-none-cookies value.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Blink component
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Chromium &gt; Blink &gt; SecurityFeature &gt; ContentSecurityPolicy
