&gt;&gt;&gt; Summary
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; When a navigation is initiated by an Element (i.e., a link click or a
&gt;&gt;&gt; form submission), the sourceElement property on the NavigateEvent will be
&gt;&gt;&gt; the initiating element.
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Blink component Blink&gt;History
&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://issues.chromium.org/issues?q=customfield1222907:%22Blink%3EHistory%22"&gt;https://issues.chromium.org/issues?q=customfield1222907:%22Blink%3EHistory%22&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
