&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20241120" rel="nofollow"&gt;Wed, 20 Nov 2024 13:05:05 -0800&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
